<br />

<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
  <a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fnLe9pEPqDw/Xte8zmmqSRI/AAAAAAAAAbc/VfVuYeLl9p4yp1on6YrkxJEUWJ4pYxP5wCK4BGAsYHg/books_1.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
    <img alt="wall of books" border="0" data-original-height="341" data-original-width="512" height="266" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fnLe9pEPqDw/Xte8zmmqSRI/AAAAAAAAAbc/VfVuYeLl9p4yp1on6YrkxJEUWJ4pYxP5wCK4BGAsYHg/w400-h266/books_1.jpg" width="400" />
  </a>
</div>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: center;">
  <i>
    "What we really need is not more authors,<br />
    or better publishers.<br />
    What we most need is a vastly better system<br />
    to identify the books we will love."<br />
  </i>
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; text-align: center;">
  <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2016/01/16/book-it-baby/" style="color: #b4445c;" target="_blank">
    <span style="font-size: medium; font-weight: bold">TechCrunch</span>
  </a>
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  Beantown Web has developed such a system. For the 12th year running Beantown Web has conducted a quasi-scientific meta-search to identify the best business books published during the calendar year. These books are most likely to add value to your career.
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  This year's search began by identifying nine "Best of" lists. This resource list is available upon request. Presented here are the results.
</p>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  A total of 157 books were mentioned on at least one "Best of" list. Of these recommendations, 127 were mentioned only once. The remaining 30 books found their way onto at least two of the nine "Best of" lists.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: arial; font-size: large; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;">
  The Honorable Mention Shelf
</h3>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  Twenty of the 30 final candidates were mentioned on two "Best of" lists. These books have attained <b>Honorable Mention</b> status.
</p>

<h3 style="font-family: arial; font-size: large; margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: left;">
  The Must-Read Shelf
</h3>

<p style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  Seven of the remaining 10 books were mentioned on three "Best of" lists and have attained <b>Must-Read</b> status.
</p>

<ul style="font-family: arial; font-size: medium; text-align: left;">
  <li>
    <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41104077-invisible-women" target="_blank">
