    </a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/44149967-kochland" target="_blank">
      <b>Kochland</b>
    </a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43848929-talking-to-strangers" target="_blank">
      <b>Talking to Strangers</b>
    </a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/26195941-the-age-of-surveillance-capitalism" target="_blank">
      <b>The Age of Surveillence Capitalism</b>
    </a>
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/38390751-the-infinite-game" target="_blank">
