month, and enhance your business knowledge now that you have some extra time as a result of working from home!</font></div></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">The 20 books on <b>The Honorable Mention Shelf</b> (those mentioned on two "Best of" lists)&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">are being counted down over the next 20 days on Gene Babon's Twitter page&nbsp;</span><a href="https://twitter.com/genebabon" style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #7d181e; font-family: arial; font-size: large; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"><b>@genebabon</b></a><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">&nbsp;and Beantown Web's Facebook page&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/beantownweb/posts/" style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #7d181e; font-family: arial; font-size: large; text-decoration-line: none;" target="_blank"><b>@beantownweb</b></a><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">.</span></div><div><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;"><br /></span></div><div><span style="background-color: #fefdfa; color: #333333; font-family: arial; font-size: large;">View recent&nbsp;<a href="https://beantownweb.blogspot.com/search/label/books" style="color: #7d181e; text-decoration-line: none;"><b>Best Business Books blog postings</b></a>.</span></div><div><br /></div></div>
